headline: TECH Q1 Earnings Call: Management Highlights Market Uncertainties and Strategic Mitigation Efforts
summary: Life sciences company Bio-Techne (NASDAQ:TECH) met Wall Street’s revenue expectations in Q1 CY2025, with sales up 4.2% year on year to $316.2 million. Its non-GAAP profit of $0.56 per share was 10.4% above analysts’ consensus estimates.

headline: ScaleReady Announces a G-Rex® Grant has been awarded to Immuneel Therapeutics
summary: ScaleReady, in collaboration with Wilson Wolf Manufacturing, Bio-Techne Corporation and CellReady, today announced that Immuneel Therapeutics has been awarded a $150,000 G-Rex® Grant to support process development aimed at enhancing the scalability and cost-effectiveness of CAR-T cell manufacturing in India.
